description: Retrieves complete information about one delivery source.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the delivery source that you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: deliverySource
nested_items.description: A structure containing information about the delivery source.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The unique name of the delivery source.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) that uniquely identifies this delivery source.

nested_items.name: resourceArns
nested_items.description: This array contains the ARN of the Amazon Web Services resource that sends logs and is represented by this delivery source. Currently, only one ARN can be in the array.

nested_items.name: service
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services service that is sending logs.

nested_items.name: logType
nested_items.description: The type of log that the source is sending. For valid values for this parameter, see the documentation for the source service.
